ical account of the statement by Jordan of his canonical form\ntheorem. Further, we analyze how Poincar\\'e transformed this theorem by\nappealing to Hermite's\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2012 09:09:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-16"}
