-resolution surveys of the Galactic\nplane should be able to detect it clearly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2012 11:39:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2012 09:45:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Oct 2012 09:27:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
